The following installation notice is only supplemental and should only be used
if the the setting in simonblinks.cfg and at the top of simonblinks.py are
set appropriate.

To install it, run the following command inside this directory:

    python setup.py install

Note that this application requires Python 2.3 or later, and a recent
version of Pygame. You can obtain Python from http://www.python.org/ and
Pygame from http://www.pygame.org/.

Please have a look at the README for usage instructions.
